{"sections":{"main":{"type":"page-default","settings":{"section_width":"container","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"rich_text_9CPpMY":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_U3Uh9A":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Help Us Build a Forest – Volunteer with Us!","font_size":36,"font_weight":"heading_weight","uppercase":false,"spacing_bottom":24}}},"block_order":["heading_U3Uh9A"],"name":"t:sections.rich_text.name","settings":{"section_width":"container","color_scheme":"","content_alignment":"center","content_max_width":100,"enable_expand_content":false,"expand_content_button":"See all Information","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"rich_text_KzKPtg":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_nAMXX6":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Plant a Tree Today, Give Life for TomorroW","font_size":36,"font_weight":"heading_weight","uppercase":false,"spacing_bottom":24}},"description_8bqDPK":{"type":"description","settings":{"description":"<p>Have you ever dreamed of planting a forest but didn’t know where to start? Are you concerned about the rising pollution levels and the impact on our planet? Do you feel compelled to take action against the deteriorating living conditions? Welcome to our community! We’re on a mission to plant a forest, and we need passionate individuals like you to join us in making a meaningful impact.<br\/><br\/><\/p>","font_size":14,"font_weight":"body_weight","spacing_bottom":10}},"heading_MLPWEC":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Join Our Mission","font_size":28,"font_weight":"heading_weight","uppercase":false,"spacing_bottom":24}},"custom_html_J68P9P":{"type":"custom_html","settings":{"html_custom":"<img loading=\"eager\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"emoji\" role=\"img\" src=\"https:\/\/s.w.org\/images\/core\/emoji\/15.0.3\/svg\/1f331.svg\" alt=\"🌱\">","spacing_bottom":24}},"description_edW8tT":{"type":"description","settings":{"description":"<p>We are seeking enthusiastic volunteers who are eager to help us create community forests. Whether you can lend a hand on weekdays or weekends, we have flexible opportunities that fit your schedule. Your support is vital, whether it’s getting your hands dirty in the soil or helping us spread the word about this important initiative. The more people we can engage, the greater our impact will be!<br\/><br\/><\/p>","font_size":14,"font_weight":"body_weight","spacing_bottom":10}},"heading_zF4UaC":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Join Our Mission","font_size":28,"font_weight":"heading_weight","uppercase":false,"spacing_bottom":24}},"custom_html_MirVPz":{"type":"custom_html","settings":{"html_custom":"<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"emoji\" role=\"img\" src=\"https:\/\/s.w.org\/images\/core\/emoji\/15.0.3\/svg\/1f30d.svg\" alt=\"🌍\">","spacing_bottom":24}},"description_g9YQFx":{"type":"description","settings":{"description":"<p>Once you sign up to volunteer, our team will reach out to you to talk about how you can contribute. Don’t worry if you’re unsure about what role you can play; there’s a place for everyone in this effort. Just fill out the form below, and we’ll work together to find the best fit for your skills and interests.<\/p><p><strong>Join Our Mission 🌳<\/strong><\/p><p><\/p><p>Join us in creating a greener future for our planet. Together, we can make a difference<strong>one tree at a time!<\/strong><\/p>","font_size":14,"font_weight":"body_weight","spacing_bottom":10}}},"block_order":["heading_nAMXX6","description_8bqDPK","heading_MLPWEC","custom_html_J68P9P","description_edW8tT","heading_zF4UaC","custom_html_MirVPz","description_g9YQFx"],"name":"t:sections.rich_text.name","settings":{"section_width":"container","color_scheme":"","content_alignment":"center","content_max_width":100,"enable_expand_content":false,"expand_content_button":"See all Information","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"rich_text_Nez7jU":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"description_yEaaYN":{"type":"descri